subject: After getting the details from
body:
After getting the details from you, we carry out investigations and trace
where the funds are. The scammer would not be able to trace you. We take
between 15-20% of the total funds recovered depending on the recovery
process.
Regards,
Myprincipalchargeback.

subject: Re: After getting the details from
body:
Dear Sir/Madam,

Thank you for your response. I understand that you will trace the funds and ensure their safe recovery. However, I would like to know more about the process involved in this recovery. Could you please provide more details on how you plan to carry out this operation? 

Also, could you clarify what percentage of the total recovered funds will be taken as a fee for your services? Your previous message was not clear on this point.

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best wishes,
Phillip
